data.description: Beautifully updated 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with a spacious, open floor plan that offers warming natural light throughout. This home features new kitchen cabinets, new flooring, new hot water heater, and newer appliances! Well maintained and ready to welcome new owners.  Conveniently located with proximity to urban amenities; This quiet, comfortable, and affordable community is only $135 monthly for HOA dues which cover Water, Sewer, Garbage, and common area road maintenance. No space rent! Own your home and the land it sits on.  This home offers a low maintenance fenced backyard and a covered patio area that is perfect for entertaining.  Enjoy the beautiful nearby mountain views and watch the deer and wildlife visit right from the comfort of your home.
